Now integrating,


f(x)  = \sum_{n=0}^\infty (-1)^n 3^n \frac{x^{3n+2}}{3n+2} +C


To have f(0)=1, we need C=1. So, finally


f(x)  = 1+ \sum_{n=0}^\infty (-1)^n  \frac{3^n }{3n+2} x^{3n+2}

