\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n+1) 3^n}
&=\sqrt{3} \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n+1)\big(\sqrt{3}\big)^{2n+1} }


& =\sqrt{3} \sum_{n=0}^\infty (-1)^n\frac{x^{2n+1}}{2n+1}
