\amp\hskip0.5in=
	\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n+1)!}\left[\left(\frac{\pi}{4}\right)^{2n+1}+\left(\frac{\pi}{2}\right)^{2n+1} \right]

	&\hskip0.5in=\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n+1)!}\left(\frac{\pi}{4}\right)^{2n+1}
